---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/content.css';
---
<BaseLayout title="Healthcare Equipment Field Inventory Software — iPad Capture | Estrelis.ai" description="Capture existing hospital equipment with iPad. 360-degree panoramic photos, barcode scanning, and AI asset identification for healthcare facility assessments and renovation planning.">

  <section class="content-hero">
    <h1>iPad-Powered Field Equipment Inventory</h1>
    <p>Capture existing equipment data in the field with an iPad. 360-degree panoramic photos, barcode scanning, and AI-powered asset identification — purpose-built for healthcare facilities.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Why Field Inventory Matters</h2>
    <p>Accurate equipment data is the foundation of every renovation and replacement project. Yet most healthcare organizations rely on outdated asset management records, incomplete spreadsheets, or expensive third-party inventories. Estrelis puts the power of field capture directly in the hands of your planning team.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Field Capture Capabilities</h2>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>360° Panoramic Room Capture</h3>
        <p>Capture full panoramic photos of every room with Insta360 integration. Reviewers can virtually walk through spaces and verify equipment without returning to the facility.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Barcode and Label Scanning</h3>
        <p>Scan asset tags, serial numbers, and manufacturer labels. Data is instantly associated with the room and linked to catalog records.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>AI Asset Identification</h3>
        <p>AI recognizes common medical equipment from photos and suggests catalog matches. Reduces manual data entry and ensures consistent equipment classification.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Offline-First Design</h3>
        <p>Works in hospital environments where WiFi is unreliable or restricted. Data syncs automatically when connectivity is restored.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>From Field to Planning</h2>
    <p>Field inventory data flows directly into Estrelis project planning. Captured equipment is automatically matched to catalog items, assessed for condition and lifecycle status, and incorporated into renovation budgets — no re-keying required.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Captured items auto-matched to equipment catalog</li>
      <li>Condition assessment and lifecycle status tracking</li>
      <li>Panoramic photos accessible from project planning views</li>
      <li>Export inventory data to Excel for stakeholder review</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Need to inventory existing equipment?</h2>
    <p>See how Estrelis makes field capture fast and accurate.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Request a Demo</a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
